$AAPL - `Heres a tip for anyone having trouble with entering positions, I do it sometimes & I actually did it yesterday with AAPL.`

**Pyramiding into a Trend trade**
Dont take the full position at once if you find yourself very stressed after placing trades because you oversized.

**1.** Buy 25% on the initial signal
**2.** Add another 50% on confirmation of the signal 
**3.** Add another 25% on follow through of price action 

**Build your position one step at a time, add to winners & cut losers short. You notice I dont average down and theres a reason for that.**
